OL,3,CTransport strike called off after
OL,4,Cimproved pay offer
OL,6,FThree days of public transport strikes
OL,7,Fhave been called off after workers
OL,8,Fwere given an improved pay offer.
OL,9,FThousands of Translink workers on bus
OL,10,Fand rail services were due to walk out
OL,11,Ffrom midnight on Tuesday following the
OL,12,Frejection of an "inadequate pay
OL,13,Foffer".JHowever, the public transport
OL,14,Ftrade unions have suspended the strike
OL,15,Faction following an improved pay offer
OL,16,Ffrom the company.
