OL,6,FIt comes after Unite, GMB and Siptu
OL,7,Freconvened talks with Translink on
OL,8,FSunday.JThe three unions are to ballot
OL,9,Ftheir members on the new offer.JTrain
OL,10,Fand bus drivers participated in a
OL,11,Fnumber of days of strike action before
OL,12,FChristmas, bringing public transport
OL,13,Fservices to a halt across Northern
OL,14,FIreland.JTranslink workers also took
OL,15,Fpart in one of the largest strikes in
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland's history last month,
OL,17,Finvolving workers from multiple public
OL,18,Fsectors.JLast week, Stormont ministers
OL,19,Fagreed to release #688 million to make
OL,20,Foutstanding pay awards for public
OL,21,Fsector workers in Northern Ireland.
OL,22,FIndividual departments have each been
OL,23,Fgiven an allocation to negotiate with
OL,24,Frelevant trade unions on the pay rises
OL,25,Fthat will be introduced.JHowever,
OL,26,Funrest among unions seeking pay parity
