OL,6,FTranslink has welcomed this decision.
OL,8,FThe Infrastructure Minister welcomed
OL,9,Fthe move.JJohn O'Dowd said: "Resolving
OL,10,Fpublic sector pay quickly has been a
OL,11,Fkey priority for the Executive.
OL,13,F"This is a positive development which
OL,14,FI very much welcome.
OL,16,F"I want to thank the Unions and
OL,17,FTranslink management for their
OL,18,Fdetermination to find a resolution to
OL,19,Fthis dispute."
